473
00:53:53.674 --> 00:53:55.897
- Bom dia, Robert.
- Bom dia.


474
00:53:58.936 --> 00:54:01.872
- Boa noite e obrigada.
- Espera!


475
00:54:02.317 --> 00:54:05.469
